articles.author: Ewan Murray
articles.title: Rain leaves Brooks Koepka to lead marathon Masters finale on Sunday - The Guardian
articles.description: Brooks Koepka, who leads Jon Rahm by four shots, completed only six holes of his third round at the Masters before rain stopped play
